Vague requirement
The system should allow users to manage their notes.
Clarified requirement
Registered users should be able to create, view, update, and delete their own notes through the Notes API. A note must have a title and description. Notes created by a user should be visible only to that user. Users should not be able to create, update, retrieve, or delete notes without authentication.
Business rules
Only authenticated users can manage notes.
A user can create a note with a valid title and description.
Title and description are mandatory.
After creation, the note should appear in the user’s notes list.
A user can retrieve details of their own note.
A user can update the title and description of their own note.
A user can delete their own note.
Deleted notes should no longer appear in the notes list.
A user cannot manage another user’s notes.

